About
With more than 400 stores, this mall truly caters to all audiences and budgets. Find international brands like Lululemon and Desigual as well as more local labels including Almotahajiba and Hanayen.

Less crowded and budget friendly.
Jul 2024 • Family
Mirdif Mall is a charming spot, albeit smaller and not as modern as some of the other malls. It exudes a certain old-world charm and offers plenty of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options for kids. It's also more affordable compared to other malls, and you'll notice more local patrons here. If you're looking for a less crowded, budget-friendly mall away from the tourist hustle and bustle, this is the place to go.
Written July 19, 2024
